data.description: This beautiful single-story home showcases vinyl wood tone flooring in the entry, great room, kitchen and dining area.  Open concept with a welcoming kitchen that showcases white shaker cabinets with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Primary bedroom is tucked away at the back of the home offering plenty of privacy. $41,500 in upgrades included.
